00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:06.079
sister Agapeta Reyes set a beautiful example

00:05:06.079 --> 00:05:09.379
in building up the faith of her children.

00:05:09.379 --> 00:05:18.980
What circumstances made that effort a special challenge?

00:05:18.980 --> 00:05:24.170
It's not easy raising kids in the truth,

00:05:24.170 --> 00:05:30.879
and I had ten.

00:05:30.879 --> 00:05:33.980
I learned the truth when I was 19.

00:05:33.980 --> 00:05:36.279
Some witnesses came to preach in our town

00:05:36.279 --> 00:05:39.579
and my father offered them a place to stay.

00:05:39.579 --> 00:05:42.079
He spoke with them all through the night

00:05:42.079 --> 00:05:45.680
and then announced excitedly that he had found the truth.

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:49.879
Eventually, I was baptized in the 1950s.

00:05:49.879 --> 00:05:52.579
