00:06:02.480 --> 00:06:06.279
I understood that I needed to be in subjection to my husband

00:06:06.279 --> 00:06:08.879
with the hope that he could be won over without a word

00:06:08.879 --> 00:06:11.279
by means of my conduct.

00:06:11.279 --> 00:06:12.779
When my children were young,

00:06:12.779 --> 00:06:16.480
I made a weekly Bible study program for each of them.

00:06:16.480 --> 00:06:18.680
And as they grew up, the older kids helped me

00:06:18.680 --> 00:06:21.480
with their younger siblings.

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:22.480
I remember, Mom,

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:25.680
always made an effort to teach me how to preach.

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:28.079
I would write presentations for the ministry

00:06:28.079 --> 00:06:29.980
on pieces of paper,

00:06:29.980 --> 00:06:31.279
and the kids would practice

00:06:31.279 --> 00:06:34.180
while they did their chores around the house.

00:06:34.180 --> 00:06:38.379
We set aside time one day a week for our family study.

00:06:38.379 --> 00:06:40.980
You could be anything, a sack of potatoes,

00:06:40.980 --> 00:06:43.279
a sack of flour, or a house plant.

00:06:43.279 --> 00:06:44.279
She would tell me,

00:06:44.279 --> 00:06:47.680
imagine that this is a person you meet and feel serious.

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:49.279
What would you say to them?

00:06:49.279 --> 00:06:51.379
When I finished, she would say to me,

00:06:51.379 --> 00:06:53.079
the way you did it just now,

00:06:53.079 --> 00:06:56.279
do it like that when you go out in the ministry.

00:06:56.279 --> 00:07:00.980
My mom was very creative.

00:07:00.980 --> 00:07:06.519
She would assign us to play the part of different Bible characters.

00:07:07.519 --> 00:07:13.519
My mom taught us to appreciate the truth through her example.

00:07:13.519 --> 00:07:16.920
I served as a regular pioneer for many years,

00:07:16.920 --> 00:07:20.920
and I encouraged my kids to reach out for spiritual goals.

00:07:20.920 --> 00:07:23.220
My daughter left home at the age of 18

00:07:23.220 --> 00:07:25.819
to serve as a special pioneer.

00:07:25.819 --> 00:07:28.519
