00:07:28.519 --> 00:07:31.019
These two proved to be excellent examples

00:07:31.019 --> 00:07:34.220
for their younger brothers.

00:07:34.220 --> 00:07:37.220
Raising my son, Noe, was a challenge.

00:07:37.220 --> 00:07:39.720
